Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram showing the dynamic interactions for connectivity in the fredrikhgrelland_data-mesh system:

```plantuml
@startuml fredrikhgrelland_data-mesh

participant "User" as User
participant "SQLPad" as SQLPad
participant "Consul" as Consul
participant "Presto" as Presto
participant "Hive Metastore" as Hive
participant "MinIO" as MinIO

User -> SQLPad: Execute SQL query
activate SQLPad

SQLPad -> Consul: Discover Presto service
activate Consul
Consul --> SQLPad: Return Presto service details
deactivate Consul

SQLPad -> Presto: Submit SQL query
activate Presto

Presto -> Consul: Discover Hive Metastore service
activate Consul
Consul --> Presto: Return Hive Metastore service details
deactivate Consul

Presto -> Hive: Request metadata
activate Hive
Hive --> Presto: Return metadata
deactivate Hive

Presto -> Consul: Discover MinIO service
activate Consul
Consul --> Presto: Return MinIO service details
deactivate Consul

Presto -> MinIO: Request data
activate MinIO
MinIO --> Presto: Return data
deactivate MinIO

Presto --> SQLPad: Return query results
deactivate Presto

SQLPad --> User: Display query results
deactivate SQLPad

@enduml
```